                            "content": "<h1><em><span style=\"color:#FF8C00;\">Voor de werkgroep</span></em></h1>\n<h1> </h1>\n<p>De documenten staan in deze drive:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1Em1XYLLDt9KZ-vcr8LWqPdvzGU9S4LJA?usp=sharing\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1Em1XYLLDt9KZ-vcr8LWqPdvzGU9S4LJA?usp=sharing</a></p>\n"
